"       Richard J Schanler, MD",
"      </a>",
"      <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?36/61/37845/contributors\" id=\"au1765\">",
"       Lisa Enger, RN, BSN, IBCLC",
"      </a>",
"     </td>",
"     <td>",
