"       Section Editor",
"      </a>",
"      <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?36/61/37845/contributors\" id=\"se4702\">",
"       Steven A Abrams, MD",
"      </a>",
"     </td>",
